summary: Do you think the crush is actually fully gone?
question: Do you think the crush is actually fully gone?
answer: in short, no. with the way that they dealt with the crush, in the hardly ever mentioning it until he was either coming out to someone or telling someone it was gone, i think there’s a good chance that it’s not actually fully gone. i don’t think it’s as strong as it was in season 1 and early season 2, but i think it’s still there. i think that jonah and cyrus together could be one of the most powerful endgames ever, even if it happens in the future after the show has ended. it’s just so apparent that they both care about eachother so much, and having them end up together would be such a power move on disney’s part.
